   "action": "<ACOND () (UP <TELL \"Disappointed at having found nothing of interest, Praxix climbed the\ncrumbling stairs and was soon \"> <COND (<NOT <FSET? ,CASTLE-TOWER ,SEEN>> <TELL \"atop the tower.\"> <MOVE-TO ,CASTLE-TOWER>) (T <TELL \"back at ground level.\"> <MOVE-TO ,CASTLE-BASE>)>)>",
   "descfcn": null,
