   "action": "<ACOND () (PROCEED <TELL \"The path curved toward the east along the foothills of the mountains,\nand we were soon forced to choose between climbing higher or veering\noff and into the southern valley. But there was no choice, really, since\nour goal was to the east; it would be impossible to avoid the mountains, so\nwe started our ascent.\" CR CR> <TELL \"The climb was long and arduous, and it was not until late in the second day\nthat we reached a plateau high in the mountains. But it was dark, and little\ncould be seen. And so we camped there under a starry sky.\" CR CR> <COND (<AND <NOT <IN? ,ESSENCE-FIRE ,ESSENCES>> <FSET? ,NEWHALL-PASS ,SCOUTED> <NOT <IN? ,HINT-MINAR ,HINTS>>> <HINT ,HINT-NO-FIRE>)> <NEXT-DAY 2> ;\"**Segment change\" <GATE-TO-HIGH-PLAIN>) (SCOUT:REMOVE <CAIRN-SCOUT> <RTRUE>) (BACK:REMOVE <TELL \"I suggested returning to Lavos, but the idea was immediately quashed\nby the group.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"Our destiny lies ahead, not behind,\" Praxix said. \"Try to remember that.\"\">)>",
