    "ENTER": [
     "<EXECUTE () <COND (<NOT <QSET? ,HERE ,SEEN>> <TELL \"As quietly as we could, we squeezed our way through the cleft and\nsoon came upon a wide, circular chamber with no exit other than the\none through which we had entered.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"I would swear the tapping came from here,\" \"> <COND (<IN-PARTY? ,BERGON> <TELL \"Bergon\">) (T <TELL \"Praxix\">)> <TELL \" said.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"And so would I. You don't think the pick-axe was working here on its\nown?\" I asked.\">) (<NOT <QSET? ,HERE ,EXAMINED>> <TELL \"Once again, we made our way through the cleft and into the circular\nchamber. Once again, there was nobody there.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"Doesn't make a bit of sense,\" \"> <TELL D ,PRAXIX \" said.\">)>>"
    ]
