    "CLOCK": [
     "<EXECUTE () <COND (<AND <QSET? ,HERE ,BLACK-MIX> <IN-PARTY? ,HURTH> <FSET? ,HURTH ,BUSY>> <TELL CR CR \"A moment later, it was over. Hurth, unable to breathe, died there, under the\ntree. We buried him in silence under the shade of the tree.\" CR CR> <COND (<IN-PARTY? ,ESHER> <TELL \"Esher was full of self-recriminations, feeling that he did not move quickly\nenough to help our friend. But there was little time for such thoughts, and much to\nbe done if we were to accomplish our task.\">) (T <TELL \"In truth, there was nothing to be done, having neither Esher nor Praxix here\nto help us. It had happened so suddenly, it is entirely possible that they could\nnot have done better.\">)> <FCLEAR ,HURTH ,BUSY> <UPDATE-REMOVE ,HURTH-OBJECT> <HINT ,HINT-ALLERGY> <KILLED-OFF ,HURTH>)>>"
    ]
