   "action": "<ACOND () (ACCEPT <TELL ,VERY-KIND CR CR> <CHOOSE-ELFENTIDE> <RETURN-FROM-WHARF> <END-OPTION>) (CONSIDER <TELL-CONSIDER> <MOVE-TO ,WHARF> <END-OPTION>) (LIE <TELL \"\"We're heading south, to the Isle of Estril,\" Bergon said. It\nwas a lie, of course, but at least in the right direction.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"Estril, aye,\" the captain said, \"We can take you there, and\nget in a day's fishing at that.\"\"> <OPTION ,BERGON ,ACCEPT-COMMAND ,CONSIDER-COMMAND>) (TELL-TRUTH <FSET ,HERE ,TRUTHFUL> <TELL \"\"We are headed toward the Misty Isle.\"\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"The Misty Isle,\" the captain started, \"Is that so?\" He rubbed his\nstubbled face and continued, \"There's nobody fool enough to go there;\nain't nobody ever returned. I'm sorry, lads, you'll have no luck around\nhere. Now, if you don't mind, I've got some serious work to do.\"\"> <REMOVE-TRAVEL-COMMAND ,WHARF ,ELFENTIDE-COMMAND> <FSET ,ELFENTIDE ,DEAD> <MOVE-TO ,WHARF> <END-OPTION>)>",
