     "<EXECUTE () <FSET ,HERE ,SEEN> <TELL CR CR \"As we approached, he smiled broadly and welcomed us aboard. \"Name's\nStegg,\" he said, \"and this here's my boat. Mighty proud of her, I\nam.\"\" CR CR> <TELL ,NEED-BOAT CR CR> <TELL \"\"That's my business,\" Stegg replied. \"Where is it then that you're\nbound?\"\"> <CHECK-FOREBODING> <OPTION ,BERGON ,TELL-TRUTH-COMMAND ,LIE-COMMAND>>"
