     "<EXECUTE () <COND (<AND <FSET? ,BEND-WILL-SPELL ,TRAPPED> <NOT <QSET? ,BEND-WILL-SPELL ,DEAD>> <IN-PARTY? ,ESHER>> <TELL CR CR \"Back outside, Praxix explained the odd happenings inside the inn.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"It would appear that the mixture was quite effective. You see, Esher\nhad just made one of his typically insulting remarks, and I, not\nunnaturally, became angry. But what I was fantasizing, the innkeeper actually\ndid! I have not heard of such a mind-controlling spell, but I cannot doubt its\npower.\" CR CR> <TELL \"We could not fault Esher for his lack of enthusiasm. \"I don't suppose\nthere might have been another way to find this out?\" he asked.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"None that I am aware of,\" Praxix replied, with just the slightest hint\nof a smile.\">)>>"
