    "TEXT": [
     "<EXECUTE () <TELL \"\"Where am I?\" Praxix asked, thinking it might help. It didn't.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"You're here with me,\" the tree replied.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"And where would that be?\" Praxix tried.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"In the forest?\" the tree replied uncertainly, trying his best to be\nhelpful.\" CR CR> <TELL \"Praxix slumped to the ground, rubbing his head. This was shaping up to\nbe a miserable day, he thought. Best to leave this leaf-laden philosopher\nand try to find the others.\">>"
    ]
