   "action": "<ACOND () (INVENTORY <TELL \"Praxix took stock of his possessions finding \"> <COND (<NOT <LIST-CONTENTS ,INVENTORY>> <TELL \"only\">) (T <TELL \" and\">)> <TELL \" his magical paraphenalia - his staff and pouch of powders.\"> <UPDATE-FSET ,HERE ,INVENTORIED>) (DROP <COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,XFER-1-ANTE ,XFER-2-ANTE ,XFER-3-ANTE> <UPDATE-MOVE ,ACTION-OBJECT <COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,XFER-1-ANTE> ,XFER-1) (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,XFER-2-ANTE> ,XFER-2) (T ,XFER-3)>> <TELL \"Thinking it might be helpful, Praxix dropped the \" AO \" over the railing and\ndown to the bottom of the pit, where it landed \"> <COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,XFER-1-ANTE> <TELL \"almost immediately.\">) (T <TELL \"more than a couple of seconds later.\"> <TELL CR CR \"\"An awfully long way down,\" he said, gazing absently into the abyss.\">)>) (T <TELL \"Praxix thought to drop the \" AO \", but felt it imprudent to do so.\">)>)>",
