   "action": "<EXECUTE () <COND (<NOT ,A-B-FLAG> <TELL \"Perhaps taking the northern path in the forest would have prevented\nus from walking into the orcs' trap.\"> <UPDATE-REMOVE ,HINT-ORC-TRAP>) (<NOT <FSET? ,MINE-JUNCTION ,SEEN>> <TELL \"Why we did not fully explore the lower chambers remains a mystery.\"> <UPDATE-REMOVE ,HINT-ORC-TRAP>) (<NOT <QSET? ,ACTIVE-MINE ,SOLVED>> <TELL \"We never did discover the meaning of the tapping sounds in the mine.\nIt may have been worthwhile to check them out again.\">) (<FSET? ,RED-ROCK ,SOLVED> <TELL \"I'm certain the red rock I recovered from the mine was the key to the\nminer's disappearances! Could we have used it to save \" D ,TRAP-VICTIM \" from the orcs?\"> <COND (<NOT <FSET? ,RED-ROCK ,DEAD>> <TELL \" I think I had the rocks with me, though I would have had to check\nmy inventory to be sure.\">)> <UPDATE-REMOVE ,HINT-ORC-TRAP>) (<NOT <IN? ,RED-ROCK ,ACTIVE-MINE>> <TELL \"Did we fail to pay close enough attention to the mine itself;\ndid we examine everything?\"> <UPDATE-REMOVE ,HINT-ORC-TRAP>) (T <TELL \"The miner surely knew many things. Did we ask him enough questions?\"> <UPDATE-REMOVE ,HINT-ORC-TRAP>)>>",
   "descfcn": null,
