   "adjectives": [],
   "action": "<EXECUTE () <COND (<NOT <FSET? ,BLACK-REAGENT ,SEEN>> <TELL \"It was foolish to attempt to get past the mudwargs. Why didn't we stay\nwith Umber and seek his advice?\">) (,BLACK-COUNT <TELL \"The black reagent frightened Praxix, I am sure. Nevertheless, he might\nhave experimented more with the various combinations of mixtures.\">) (T <TELL \"I will never understand why Praxix never experimented with the black\nreagent. Perhaps he had his reasons, but I have never understood what\nthey could be.\">)> <UPDATE-REMOVE ,HINT-MUDWARGS>>",
   "descfcn": null,
   "contfcn": null,
   "globals": [],
   "pseudo": [],
