     "<EXECUTE () <TELL CR \"The bandits, finding the fight more than they had bargained for,\nretreated out of sight.\"> <COND (<FSET? ,BANDITS-FIGHT ,SEEN> <COND (,BANDITS-SPELL <UNUSE-ESSENCES ,BANDITS-SPELL> <SETG BANDITS-SPELL <>> <TELL \" Praxix, seeing that there was no need for his magic, put away his pouch.\">)> <CLEAR-BUSY> <TELL \" A moment later, \"> <COND (<FSET? ,MINAR ,SEEN> <TELL \"Minar\">) (T <TELL \"the man we had seen entering the tavern\">)> <TELL \" appeared, bow in\nhand. \"I thought you might be needing some help,\" he said, grinning.\" CR CR> <COND (<FSET? ,MINAR ,SEEN> <TELL \"\"My previous offer stands, and this time I would advise you to\naccept it.\" He stood there, grinning all the time, waiting for our\nanswer.\">) (T <TELL ,MINAR-INTRO>)> <OPTION ,LEADER ,ACCEPT-COMMAND ,DECLINE-COMMAND ,GET-ADVICE-COMMAND>) (T <END-COMBAT <>>)> <RTRUE>>"
