   "action": "<ACOND () (EXAMINE:REMOVE <COND (<EQUAL? ,ACTOR ,PRAXIX> <TELL \"At Bergon's request, Praxix looked over the cairn. \"The cairn was\nmade by our people and not by the locals from Lavos,\" he said.\">) (T <TELL \"\"This cairn looks like one of ours,\" \" ACT \" said, looking over the mound\nof carefully piled rocks. \"Not at all like those we passed on the outskirts\nof Lavos.\"\">)>)>",
