   "action": "<ACOND () (EXAMINE:CLEAR <TELL ACT \" took a tentative step forward and touched the polished stone with his\nhand. Breathlessly, he lifted the lid and stood there, frozen with\nfear. \"\"> <GRAPHIC ,G-CEDRITH> <COND (<EQUAL? ,ACTOR ,PRAXIX> <TELL \"Why, this is quite remarkable,\" he said excitedly.\">) (T <TELL \"I cannot believe it,\" he said in a perfect monotone.\">)> <TELL CR CR \"It was impossible, and to this day we have not found an explanation\nfor what we discovered within: a Dwarvish body, perfectly preserved\nthrough the long years. He wore a long, white robe which appeared to\nglisten in the light of Praxix' staff. Around his neck, a round white\nstone hung at the end of a golden chain.\"> <COND (<IN-PARTY? ,HURTH> <TELL CR CR \"\"Cedrith!\" gasped Hurth, stumbling backward.\">)> <UPDATE-MOVE ,SPIRIT-STONE ,HERE>)>",
