   "action": "<EXECUTE () <TELL \"\"Mudwargs?\" Bergon asked.\" CR CR> <TELL \"\"Ah, I see your point,\" Umber replied. \"You're not from here, so you and\nthe mudwargs are not well acquainted. Well, to be honest, I don't know much\nabout them myself, except that they live underground and feed during the\nday when the ground is flooded. You'll never see one at night, which is\njust fine with me, but during the daytime they can be quite trying.\"\"> <FSET ,ASK-UMBER-MUDWARGS ,SEEN> <UPDATE-REMOVE ,ASK-UMBER-MUDWARGS>>",
