   "file": "characters.zil",
   "line": 261,
   "endLine": 274,
   "source": "<ROUTINE PARTY-CHANGE (CHR1 CHR2 \"AUX\" (CNT <GET ,PARTY 0>) TMP)\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <COND (<L? .CNT 1> <RFALSE>)\n\t\t       (<EQUAL? <GET ,PARTY .CNT> .CHR1>\n\t\t\t<PUT ,PARTY .CNT .CHR2>\n\t\t\t<FSET .CHR2 ,IN-PARTY>\n\t\t\t<FCLEAR .CHR1 ,IN-PARTY>\n\t\t\t<SORT-PARTY>\n\t\t\t<NEW-CHARACTER .CHR2>\n\t\t\t<SET TMP <APPLY <GETP .CHR1 ,P?REMOVE>>>\n\t\t\t<SET TMP <APPLY <GETP .CHR2 ,P?ADD>>>\n\t\t\t<SETG UPDATE-FLAG T>\n\t\t\t<RTRUE>)>\n\t\t <SET CNT <- .CNT 1>>>>"
