   "source": "<ROUTINE O-MIX ()\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? ,ACTOR ,TAG>\n\t\t<REMOVE-MISSING-POWDERS>\n\t\t<FIND-OBJECTS ,TAG-POWDERS>)\n\t       (<AND <EQUAL? ,HERE ,ZAN-OUTSKIRTS>\n\t\t     <FSET? ,HERE ,SEEN>>\n\t\t<FIND-OBJECTS ,ESSENCES>)\n\t       (<FIRST? ,ESSENCES>\n\t\t;\"Don't have mix option if no essences left...\"\n\t\t<FIND-OBJECTS ,REAGENTS>)>>"
