  "WAVE-SAVE": {
   "name": "WAVE-SAVE",
   "kind": "constant",
   "file": "voyage.zil",
   "line": 376,
   "value": "\" Tossed with me into the tumult, it had split in two, its larger piece intact\nand floating on the waves. Grabbing hold of that precious flotsam, I pulled myself\nup and fell unconscious atop it. The next day, the storm having passed, I was found\nby passing fishermen and taken back to Zan where, after a few sleepless nights, I\nbooked passage to Lendros, and my home in the plains.\""
  },
